Download & install autohotkey (https://www.autohotkey.com/) and run "A32NX Pot ID Fix.ahk" script. 

This script will change A32NX mod's light potentiometer indices so that they can be changed via SPAD.neXt.

Once you run the script you will be prompted to specify A32NX mod install location. 


Reference: https://github.com/flybywiresim/a32nx/issues/1202

